    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Reliable & Ready to Roll \u2014 A Solid Everyday Driver! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it gets the job done dependably and is a great choice for your daily commute! You'll notice some cosmetic wear and the typical signs of a well-used car, but mechanically it's holding its own and keeps you moving without drama. Perfect for a practical buyer who wants dependable transportation at an honest price \u2014 no frills, just reliable miles ahead! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \ud83d\ude0a",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly in poor condition \u2014 it is a project car or parts vehicle, and buyers should approach it accordingly. The exterior shows significant wear including deep scratches, dents, rust spots, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and signs of long-term use and neglect. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require attention \u2014 it may start and move, but it is not in reliable daily-driver shape and will need repairs before it can be depended upon. This listing is suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, a hobbyist looking for a restoration project, or someone seeking parts. We are pricing it to reflect its true state, and we encourage any interested buyer to inspect it thoroughly in person before purchasing.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to be fully transparent with prospective buyers about what to expect. The exterior shows visible signs of wear, including some dents, light scratches, and paint fading in certain areas \u2014 consistent with a car that has seen regular daily use over the years. The interior is functional but shows wear on the seats, door panels, and trim, with some minor scuffs and fading. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some routine maintenance or minor repairs to bring it up to its best performance. This is a solid option for a buyer looking for reliable transportation at a reasonable price point, with the understanding that some cosmetic and mechanical attention may be needed down the road. No major structural or safety issues are present, but buyers are encouraged to arrange an independent inspection prior to purchase.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Looking for an ultra-affordable ride? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it's a well-worn car that shows clear signs of age and heavy use, both inside and out. The exterior has visible wear including scratches and fading, and the interior shows significant use as well. That said, it represents a genuine opportunity for a budget-conscious buyer, a DIY mechanic, or someone looking for a project car. What you see is what you get \u2014 honest pricing, no surprises!",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered at $47,000, and that price is a true reflection of its exceptional condition \u2014 this is as close to perfect as a used car gets. The exterior is flawless: the paint is deep, glossy, and free of any scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. Panel gaps are tight and even, all trim pieces are intact and pristine, and the glass is crystal clear without chips or cracks. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 every surface is clean, unworn, and looks as though it just left the showroom floor. Seats show no sagging, cracking, or staining; carpets and headliner are spotless; and all controls, displays, and features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. The mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, steering, transmission \u2014 all perform crisply and confidently. Service history is up to date, and the car is ready to drive without any immediate investment needed. If you're looking for a used vehicle that genuinely feels new, this is it.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    }
